going on out here 
out here is a frontier of sorts where fists brains and 
hard work win respect unalaska has no fulltime dentist no 
plumber no appliance repair service no doctor and no veterinarian 
to deal with scores of freeroaming mutts 
milk costs 499 a gallon a bottle of jack daniels sour mash 
